---
import Button from "../ui/Button.astro";
import Stars from "../ui/Stars.astro";
---
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="text-center mb-16">
    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">
      Real Results From Real Clients
    </h2>
    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      See what clients say about working with Rebel Ape.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Testimonials Grid -->
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
    <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
      <div class="gap-1 mb-6">
        <Stars />
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
        Their commitment to my success made me a forever client. They were quick to respond, professional, and provided excellent guidance throughout. Their insights helped me enhance my online presence.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900">
        Jessica <span class="font-bold">B.</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
      <div class="gap-1 mb-6">
        <Stars />
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
        Adam is truly so attentive to the needs of our small business. His professionalism is top notch and he was there when we needed him in an emergency. I cannot say enough about Rebel Ape! *paraphrased
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900">
        Lori <span class="font-bold">M.</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
      <div class="gap-1 mb-6">
        <Stars />
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
        Reliable and dedicated to their craft. Precise suggestions that drove huge impact on our business with creative and thoughtful design. They truly understand how to speak to our audience.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900">
        Jacob <span class="font-bold">M.</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonial 4 -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
      <div class="gap-1 mb-6">
        <Stars />
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
        I have worked with Adam's team for years and always find them to be great at what they do. They're responsive, reliable, and truly invested in your success. Great team! *paraphrased
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900">
        Jeff <span class="font-bold">R.</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonial 5 -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
      <div class="gap-1 mb-6">
        <Stars />
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
        Rebel Ape is incredible to work with. Very collaborative, genuinely invested in outcomes, and a pleasure to partner with on projects. *paraphrased
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900">
        Bryan <span class="font-bold">H.</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonial 6 -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
      <div class="gap-1 mb-6">
        <Stars />
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
        Adam is amazing at what he does and his customer service is stellar. So happy with his service and he's a great person to work with. I strongly recommend using Adam! *paraphrased
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900">
        Jack <span class="font-bold">B.</span>
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
    <div class="mt-16 text-center">
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        Ready to start working on your leads? Let's get started on your next project.
      </p>
      <div class="flex justify-center">
        <Button text="Schedule a Call" icon="phone" href="https://schedule.therebelape.com" />
      </div>
    </div>
    
</div>
